text: Jędrzej Maćkowiak (born 17 October 1992) is a Polish volleyball player, a member of Polish club Krispol Września, 2014 Polish Champion. ==Career== Maćkowiak is an alumnus of Skra Bełchatów. He debuted in first squad of PGE Skra in season 2012/2013. On May 27, 2014 his team won a title of Polish Champion after final matches against Asseco Resovia Rzeszów.PGE Skra mistrzem Polski - plusliga.pl - 27-04-2014 In June 2014 went to Effector Kielce.Maćkowiak oficjalnie w Effectorze Kielce - skra.pl - 26-06-2014 ==Sporting achievements== ===Clubs=== ====National championships==== * 2012/2013 16px Polish SuperCup2012, with PGE Skra Bełchatów * 2013/2014 16px Polish Championship, with PGE Skra Bełchatów ==References== ==External links== * PlusLiga profile Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Bełchatów Category:Sportspeople from Łódź Voivodeship Category:Polish men's volleyball players Category:Polish Champions of men's volleyball Category:Skra Bełchatów players Category:Effector Kielce players
